     The entire time during my viewing of the second movie all I could think was &quot;Wow, they took everything in the first one and made it bigger, longer, and more obsurd&quot;. It's &quot;sequel syndrome&quot;, you've got a big hit on your hands you don't want to screw it up but you also run the risk of being too boring. It looked like they did all the fight scenes and then threw in all the stuff about the matrix to try and continue the story.<br>
